{"sectionId":929,"sectionIdLiteral":"929","humanId":"song-2-intro","volumeId":"song","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"chapterTitle":{"inlineNumber":"2.","title":"Forgiveness"},"title":"Introduction"},"annotation":"S-2.in","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text song-2-intro\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"929#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Forgiveness offers wings to prayer, to make its rising easy and its progress swift.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Without its strong support it would be vain to try to rise above prayer’s bottom step, or even to attempt to climb at all.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Forgiveness is prayer’s ally; sister in the plan for your salvation.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Both must come to hold you up and keep your feet secure; your purpose steadfast and unchangeable.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>Behold the greatest help that God ordained to be with you until you reach to Him.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Illusion’s end will come with this.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>Unlike the timeless nature of its sister, prayer, forgiveness has an end.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>For it becomes unneeded when the rising up is done.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:9\"><span class=\"snr\">9</span>Yet now it has a purpose beyond which you cannot go, nor have you need to go.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:10\"><span class=\"snr\">10</span>Accomplish this and you have been redeemed.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:11\"><span class=\"snr\">11</span>Accomplish this and you have been transformed.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"929#1:12\"><span class=\"snr\">12</span>Accomplish this and you will save the world.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Forgiveness offers wings to prayer, to make its rising easy and its progress swift. Without its strong support it would be vain to try to rise above prayer’s bottom step, or even to attempt to climb","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Forgiveness: Introduction | ACIM","seoDescription":"✨ A Course in Miracles. Read “Forgiveness: Introduction” from the Song of Prayer (S-2.in): Forgiveness offers wings to prayer, to make its rising easy and its progress swift. Without its…","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Song of Prayer","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":922,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","prayer-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"2. Forgiveness","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":929,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","forgiveness-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Introduction","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":929,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","forgiveness-introduction"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Song of Prayer","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":922,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","prayer-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"2. Forgiveness","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":929,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","forgiveness-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Introduction","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":929,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","forgiveness-introduction"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Song of Prayer","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":922,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","prayer-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"2. Forgiveness","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":929,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","forgiveness-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Introduction","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":929,"slugs":["song-of-prayer","forgiveness-introduction"]}}],"slugs":["song-of-prayer","forgiveness-introduction"],"canonicalLink":"https://acim.org/acim/song-of-prayer/forgiveness-introduction/en/s/929","li